 nursing students.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">However, it is essential to thoroughly research universities, compare program offerings, consider the cost of living, and evaluate eligibility requirements before deciding.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1813\" src=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/canada-flag-female-doctor-with-stethoscope-national-healthcare-system-1.jpg\" alt=\"studying nursing\" width=\"1283\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/canada-flag-female-doctor-with-stethoscope-national-healthcare-system-1.jpg 1283w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/canada-flag-female-doctor-with-stethoscope-national-healthcare-system-1-300x140.jpg 300w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/canada-flag-female-doctor-with-stethoscope-national-healthcare-system-1-1024x479.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/canada-flag-female-doctor-with-stethoscope-national-healthcare-system-1-768x359.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1283px) 100vw, 1283px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #333333;\">What are the Top Universities to Study Nursing in 2023?<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">The QS World University Rankings by Subject 2023 provide valuable insights into the best universities for studying nursing worldwide.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Here are the top 10 universities for nursing, based on their respective scores:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">University of Pennsylvania, United States<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">King&#8217;s College London, United Kingdom<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Johns Hopkins University, United States<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">University of Washington, United States<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span styl